-- Kobe Hires Banks for a 10 Billion Yen Sale of Five-Year Bonds
-- B y   Y u s u k e   M i y a z a w a
-- 2012-05-14T03:36:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-14/kobe-hires-banks-for-a-10-billion-yen-sale-of-five-year-bonds.html
City of Kobe hired Nomura Holdings
Inc., Daiwa Securities Group Inc. and  Mizuho Financial Group
Inc. (8411)  for a 10 billion yen sale of five-year bonds, according to
an e-mailed statement from Nomura.  To contact the reporter on this story:
